O.. Oh!

15
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:13,970
Well, Yawara-san is at Kazamatsuri-san's 
place again.

16
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,690
Darnit, that Kazamatsuri!

17
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,570
Just because he's a little good at English..!

18
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:27,230
Matsuda-san, is this really sports coverage?

19
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:31,360
Seems more to me like the thing 
you hate -- a celebrity stakeout.

20
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:31,540
