the century is in question!


25
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,210
This is an outright news coverage!

26
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,080
What the heck are you thinking, anyway?

27
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,940
Good evening, Sayaka-san.

28
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:21,550
Well, what a coincidence!

29
00:03:21,690 --> 00:03:23,970
It's going to be an interesting night!

30
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:28,540
Oh yes! We should all go out to dinner!

31
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:31,290
I recently found a great restaurant.

32
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:32,720
How about it, Sayaka-san?

33
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:39,060
You're such a DOROBO-NEKO.
[Dorobo-neko -- cat thief]

34
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:43,760
You want someone else's thing that badly?

35
00:03:44,940 --> 00:03:45,730
How immoral!

36
00:03:46,170 --> 00:03:47,720
I was just...

37
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:55,320
Yes, she couldn't study at her house, so I offered to tutor her in my room, that's all.


38
00:03:56,410 --> 00:03:58,080
What an obvious lie.

39
00:03:58,170 --> 00:04:00,820
So you want Kazamatsuri-san, 
no matter what?

40
