That's not what I wanted to do.

41
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:08,230
Now listen carefully.

42
00:04:08,670 --> 00:04:12,900
Kazamatsuri-san will graduate soon and become part of the Hon'ami Group.

43
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:15,420
