Kazamatsuri-san.

52
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:14,450
Thank you for tutoring me.

53
00:05:15,220 --> 00:05:16,780
U.. umm..

54
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,280
Yawara-san.

55
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,050
Goodnight.

56
00:05:40,670 --> 00:05:42,320
Brrr, it's so cold!

57
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:50,250
Y.. Yawara-san?

58
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:56,410
Yawara-san, what's wrong?


59
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,470
Wh.. what's wrong, Yawara-san?

60
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,720
Yawara-san?

61
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,000
Yawara-san!

62
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:13,040
Kazamatsuri, why you...!

63
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:22,160
