64
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:48,460
Oh, the third-rate newspaper reporter.

65
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:51,140
Hon'ami Sayaka! You were here, too?

66
00:06:51,910 --> 00:06:54,720
Your girlfriend is quite a girl.

67
00:06:54,970 --> 00:06:56,510
Quite a girl?

68
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:58,290
Wh.. what the heck is that?

69
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:03,130
Kazamatsuri-san, I won't tell
Daddy about today.

70
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:09,210
But, don't ever get lured by her again. 
Please keep your guard up.

71
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,860
Well then, goodbye.

72
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,200
Kazamatsuri!

73
00:07:19,370 --> 00:07:21,160
What did you do to Yawara-san?

74
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,720
She was crying!

75
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,550
I don't need to discuss private matters 
with newspaper reporters.

76
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:29,830
Y.. You better not have done anything heinous!

77
00:07:30,110 --> 00:07:32,170
How rude! I'm not that kind of guy!

78
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:35,930
Besides, with Sayaka-san here, 
I couldn't have possibly done that!

79
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:36,980
You sure?

80
00:07:37,050 --> 00:07:37,980
I'm sure!

81
00:07:37,990 --> 00:07:39,440
You really sure?

82
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:40,890
Really sure!

83
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:43,200
You really really sure?

84
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,130
Enough!

85
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:50,030
Anyway, this has nothing to do with you. 
Go home! Goodbye!

86
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,070
W.. wait up!

87
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:56,320
Darnit...!

88
00:08:08,450 --> 00:08:09,600
Kazamatsuri-san..

89
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,540
Kazamatsuri-san..

90
00:08:19,380 --> 00:08:22,420
Kazamatsuri-san, you were 
Sayaka-san's fiance?

91
00:08:37,450 --> 00:08:41,050
Seishin-kan Women's Judo Cup

92
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:45,550
Ippon! 
[Ippon -- Victory!]

93
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:49,690
Ippon!

94
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,700
Ippon!

95
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:59,690
Champion! Inokuma Yawara, 1st Degree, won this tournament with all ippon victories!

96
