Since your debut, you've won 
7 tournaments so far!

100
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:23,470
You're on a roll!

101
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:25,950
Are you going to run straight
to the Barcelona Olympics?

102
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:28,110
I don't really care about the Olympics..

103
00:09:28,270 --> 00:09:30,780
You're now invincible in Japan.

104
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,270
Is the world the next level --

105
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:32,780
Is the world the next level --
I won't let you do that.

106
00:09:32,780 --> 00:09:33,930
I won't let you do that.

107
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:38,380
Ho.. Hon'ami Sayaka!

108
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:40,860
Sayaka-san.

109
00:09:41,610 --> 00:09:45,080
I've let Inokuma-san run loose a bit too long.

110
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:49,780
So I entered the next tournament.

111
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:57,040
Enjoy this moment, it won't last much longer.

112
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,200
Will it be her revenge for the 
Martial Arts Hall Defeat!?

