Will it be her revenge for the 
Martial Arts Hall Defeat!?
Hon'ami Sayaka's 
Bold Challenge 
to the 
Undefeated
Inokuma Yawara

114
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:18,100
That Miss sure is something!

115
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:25,860
"After the around-the-world training
tour, Inokuma Yawara isn't 
intimidating enough," it says.

116
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:29,970
Talk about confidence! But, 
that upfront confidence!

117
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:34,500
I really like that about that Miss.

118
00:10:36,170 --> 00:10:38,490
Yawara! You can learn a lot from her attitude!

119
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:41,050
Grandpa, hurry up and eat.

120
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,490
I need to go take a practice exam.

121
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:45,360
Oh, what is this?

122
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:48,610
She said that she'd take revenge 
and defeat you in under a minute!

123
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:52,530
If you're not going to eat,
then I'm clearing the table.

124
00:10:53,050 --> 00:10:53,850
Hold it!

125
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:59,040
Yawara! You aren't thinking clearly these days.


126
00:10:59,470 --> 00:11:02,920
You're so into the newspaper that you 
haven't touched your breakfast yet!

127
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:05,260
Nope. I'm not just talking about now.

128
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:08,620
Even in yesterday's matches, you were 
doing some reckless throws.

129
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,860
No, I was doing okay in those matches.

130
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:16,010
You're having boy problems, aren't you?

131
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:16,780
Gulp!

132
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:20,610
Gotcha, didn't I? It shows clearly on your face.

133
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,600
No, it doesn't, Grandpa. 
What are you talking about?

134
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,000
No, it doesn't, Grandpa. 
What are you talking about?
Are you troubled by that KazaMIDORI?

135
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,110
Are you troubled by that KazaMIDORI?

136
00:11:26,110 --> 00:11:26,140
Are you troubled by that KazaMIDORI?
KazaMI--? It's Kazamatsuri-san!

137
00:11:26,140 --> 00:11:28,970
KazaMI--? It's Kazamatsuri-san!

138
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:33,020
Kazamatsuri, KazaMIDORI, same difference!

139
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:36,590
Stop! Quit worrying about that kind of guy!

140
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:43,530
He turns to you, then turns to Miss Sayaka, and maybe many other girls, too.

141
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:45,780
That's a perfect KazaMIDORI for you! 
[KazaMIDORI -- weather vane]

142
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:57,390
Kazamatsuri-san has nothing to do with this!


143
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,130
Forget him.

144
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:03,150
Just think about your upcoming 
match against Hon'ami Sayaka.

145
00:12:03,450 --> 00:12:05,960
Don't underestimate that Miss' tenacity.

146
00:12:06,190 --> 00:12:06,870
Geez!

147
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:10,160
Decide if you're gonna eat or read!

148
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:11,910
I'm leaving soon.

149
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:16,550
You talk just like your dead grandma, 
my beloved Kaneko.

150
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,080
Geez..

151
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,120
Jody!

152
00:12:23,260 --> 00:12:25,980
